After the Day One of Spirit Week 2014, the juniors are leading with 610 points. The seniors are second, trailing by 90 points. Stay tuned to the Paly Voice for scores and comprehensive coverage of Spirit Week. View official scores on ASB's <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/pahsasb/sw2014">website</a>.
